{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/tools/weixin-fullscreen/","webpackCompilationHash":"","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"949d0c17-8da5-5d63-b20a-99acdb4ace98","excerpt":"运营过公众号的小伙伴都知道，在公众号后台，你只能在很小的一块区域写文章，真的是胸中豪情万丈，却只能施展在方寸之间。  你能编辑的区域只有上面图中红框内这么大，旁边那么多都是信息噪音。遇到这种问题怎么办呢？有钱的话可以换个超大显示器，没钱就只能自己解决了，我属于后者。于是乎，我就写了一个 Chrome…","html":"<p>运营过公众号的小伙伴都知道，在公众号后台，你只能在很小的一块区域写文章，真的是胸中豪情万丈，却只能施展在方寸之间。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 640px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/b1f8599a4c5b0d07512011d2640c4072/6e934/weixin-editor.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 54.134815844336345%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"weixin editor\"\n        title=\"weixin editor\"\n        src=\"/static/b1f8599a4c5b0d07512011d2640c4072/e2288/weixin-editor.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/b1f8599a4c5b0d07512011d2640c4072/264cc/weixin-editor.jpg 160w,\n/static/b1f8599a4c5b0d07512011d2640c4072/f562b/weixin-editor.jpg 320w,\n/static/b1f8599a4c5b0d07512011d2640c4072/e2288/weixin-editor.jpg 640w,\n/static/b1f8599a4c5b0d07512011d2640c4072/b3ee8/weixin-editor.jpg 960w,\n/static/b1f8599a4c5b0d07512011d2640c4072/6c315/weixin-editor.jpg 1280w,\n/static/b1f8599a4c5b0d07512011d2640c4072/6e934/weixin-editor.jpg 2878w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>你能编辑的区域只有上面图中红框内这么大，旁边那么多都是信息噪音。遇到这种问题怎么办呢？有钱的话可以换个超大显示器，没钱就只能自己解决了，我属于后者。于是乎，我就写了一个 Chrome 插件，让微信编辑器支持全屏写作。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 640px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/cf72a5358a580eb03067adf37413b31c/8f97a/full.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 54.033379694019466%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"full\"\n        title=\"full\"\n        src=\"/static/cf72a5358a580eb03067adf37413b31c/e2288/full.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/cf72a5358a580eb03067adf37413b31c/264cc/full.jpg 160w,\n/static/cf72a5358a580eb03067adf37413b31c/f562b/full.jpg 320w,\n/static/cf72a5358a580eb03067adf37413b31c/e2288/full.jpg 640w,\n/static/cf72a5358a580eb03067adf37413b31c/b3ee8/full.jpg 960w,\n/static/cf72a5358a580eb03067adf37413b31c/6c315/full.jpg 1280w,\n/static/cf72a5358a580eb03067adf37413b31c/8f97a/full.jpg 2876w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>实际效果就和上图一样，把无关的信息都隐藏起来，让写作者专注于内容。终于清静了，现在文思如泉涌，谁与我争锋？</p>\n<h3>如何使用</h3>\n<p>安装之后，在浏览器右上角就会出现一个插件的图标。进入公众号后台文章编辑页面，点击这个图标，就会进入全屏模式，再次点击就会退出全屏。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 640px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/5679794c53e55093383e136938eeb5b3/1bbe8/usage.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 48.64864864864865%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"usage\"\n        title=\"usage\"\n        src=\"/static/5679794c53e55093383e136938eeb5b3/e2288/usage.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/5679794c53e55093383e136938eeb5b3/264cc/usage.jpg 160w,\n/static/5679794c53e55093383e136938eeb5b3/f562b/usage.jpg 320w,\n/static/5679794c53e55093383e136938eeb5b3/e2288/usage.jpg 640w,\n/static/5679794c53e55093383e136938eeb5b3/b3ee8/usage.jpg 960w,\n/static/5679794c53e55093383e136938eeb5b3/6c315/usage.jpg 1280w,\n/static/5679794c53e55093383e136938eeb5b3/1bbe8/usage.jpg 2146w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3>参考</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/dzWhbGRn5lBexy8k1E7uDA\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">产品经理朋友说要沉浸式写作，我给他写了个Chrome插件</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/rXfQgMioNTW6OHPpbnMEgQ\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">送你一个公众号全屏编辑插件（ Chrome ）</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/n87JszPfBA3Y7tXbOzmZ_g\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">如何获得更加沉浸式的公众号写作体验？</a></li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"微信公众号全屏写作插件","date":"2015/08/28","description":"一个可以让微信公众号后台编辑器全屏展开的 Chrome 插件。","color":"#1BAD23","cover":"weixin-fullscreen.jpg","demo":"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/微信公众号全屏写作/dehagjgefepfeldnhgalganefodnbcfk?hl=zh-CN","demoText":"前往谷歌扩展商店下载"}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/tools/weixin-fullscreen/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/tools/movielect/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"选个电影小程序"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/creative/brain-hole/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"脑洞没边儿"}}}}}